{"type":"message","id":"2bda4b33","parentId":"d2e3dc5b","timestamp":"2026-05-03T23:04:49.654Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:fc96aa3c-0bbc-43a4-84c4-7b00b0c46a7f Wiki Logging - Finn] Execute: python3 ~/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py finn\n\nThis logs recent conversations to the wiki at ~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/. Read the wiki-heartbeat.py script and follow its logic.\nCurrent time: Sunday, May 3rd, 2026 - 7:04 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-05-03 23:04 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777849489598}}
